Heya!

I know that at the moment the club is going through some changes as
some characters are gaining more prominance and others are fading
away. We have several new characters hitting the scene and history is
in the making.

If anyone is stuck or needs some suggestions feel free to write me on
or off list and I would be happy to throw around some ideas or let you
throw some at me. I have a general ideas of where things are going,
and I am doing my best to incorporate the things that I have heard you
huys say you wanted. But if something is happening that confuses you,
please do not hesitate to ask me. My door . . . or in this case my
email . . . is always open to you.

Also if I have missed responding to someone PLEAESE tap me. I can be
forgetful of some things at times :)

- Preston
